Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办去海边的话不会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去山里的话又有虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我去买泳衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:19.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我去年的泳衣大小也不合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要买新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫对身材曲线很有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是算上这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫的攻击力很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是玩具枪的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而相反藤原书记的攻击力是战车水平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,战力差距近乎绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:49.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说色诱 这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,相对而言四宫的该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜的胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去山里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:07.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海边黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:09.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人又多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:10.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还可能有鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去山里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和刚才的说法完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山里经常下雨 还有虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:18.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海边
