Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:20.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:21.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:21.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:21.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:21.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:22.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 不如让藤原书记决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！我决定吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:27.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海边啊 去海边 你懂我的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:33.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山里啊 去山里 你不会背叛我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:38.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个里面选的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:40.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:41.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:42.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说是去山里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去恐山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,恐山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,三途河畔的地狱温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多代表轮回的风车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:02.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难得去一次 也让巫女降死者的灵看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,选谁比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:08.01,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,基督 佛陀 圣德太子也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要不 等到夏天再考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
